    "headline": "GameStop pledges to pursue its takeover offer for eBay despite rejection",
    "summary": "GameStop pledged on Friday to pursue its proposed takeover ‌of eBay, even after the e-commerce firm rejected ‌an unsolicited cash-and-stock offer of about $56 billion from the videogame retailer.  GameStop CEO Ryan Cohen ‌surprised Wall Street with ⁠the offer to buy eBay in May, arguing a combined company would be a bigger ⁠competitor to Amazon and saying he would run it.  EBay rejected it the same month.",
