    "headline": "GameStop Provides Fiscal Year 2026 Outlook",
    "summary": "GRAPEVINE, Texas, June 26, 2026--GameStop Corp. (NYSE: GME) (\"GameStop\" or the \"Company\") today announced that, for the fiscal year ending January 30, 2027 (\"fiscal year 2026\"), the Company currently expects to generate Adjusted EBITDA in excess of $600 million, compared to Adjusted EBITDA of $345.4 million in fiscal year 2025.",
